readings.question: Testing Three Card spread tooltips...
readings.cardTooltip1:
Fruitfulness, initiative, action, 
            long days, clandestine, the unknown, 
            difficulty, doubt, ignorance.
readings.cardTooltip2:
Fair young man, one impelled to render 
            service; a studious youth, news, message, 
            application, reflection, meditation.
readings.cardTooltip3:
Country life, repose, concord, 
            harmony, prosperity, peace, 
            and the perfected work of these.

readings.question: Testing the One Card spread tooltips...
readings.cardTooltip1:
Work, employment, commission, craftsmanship, 
            skill in craft and business.
